- [1mDefault[0m: [36m[][0m
- [1mExample[0m: [36mrun-extra-args = ["--test-threads", "1"][0m

[1;4mRetry configuration[0m

[1;4m[36mprofile.<name>.retries[0m

- [1mType[0m: Integer or object
- [1mDescription[0m: Retry policy for failed tests.
- [1mDocumentation[0m: [34;4m[3m]8;;https://nexte.st/docs/features/retries/\Retries and flaky tests]8;;\[0m
- [1mDefault[0m: [36m0[0m
- [1mExamples[0m:
