Custom test groups are defined under [36m[test-groups.<name>][0m sections.

For detailed information, see [34;4m[3m]8;;https://nexte.st/docs/configuration/test-groups/\Test groups for mutual exclusion[0m]8;;\.

[1;4m[36mtest-groups.<name>.max-threads[0m

- [1mType[0m: Integer or string
